videos.description: Joel Berry II gets a steal but then his shot is blocked from behind by Jaren Jackson Jr. to prevent a UNC score.
videos.headline: Berry gets steal but is shut down by Jackson

videos.description: Miles Bridges drains a 3-pointer from the top of the arc for Michigan State.
videos.headline: Bridges hits a 3-pointer to extend Spartans' lead

videos.description: Kenny Williams gets a big steal, but misses the lay-in setting up Michigan State to score on a 3-pointer from Cassius Winston.
videos.headline: Michigan St. steals UNC's momentum on turnover

videos.description: Michigan State head coach Tom Izzo says his team is playing hard on defense which has been the difference in the first half against UNC.
videos.headline: Izzo likes Spartans' defense in first half

videos.description: Joel Berry II beats the buzzer before the half with a 3-pointer for the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Berry beats the buzzer with 3-pointer

videos.description: Joshua Langford hits a corner 3-pointer giving him a career high of 20 points against the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Langford reaches career-high 20 points

videos.description: Miles Bridges reaches 11 points  for Michigan State as he drives to the basket and gets a lay-in.
videos.headline: Bridges makes nice layup

videos.description: Michigan State head coach Tom Izzo says his defense was 'really really good' which was key in their 63-45 win over the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Izzo: Defense huge in win against UNC

videos.description: The Tar Heels record their worst shooting percentage in program history, and the Spartans win easily 63-45.
